SIMULATIONS

Model 0

First variant

set.seed(1)
t <- seq(0,1, length.out = 50)
rangeval <- c(min(t),max(t))
nbasis <- 30
norder <- 4

ssm0_0 <- multimodel0_0()

dt1 <- ssm0_0[[1]]@X; dt2 <- ssm0_0[[2]]@X; dt3 <- ssm0_0[[3]]@X; 

datos <- array(dim=c(100,50,3))
datos[,,1]<-dt1
datos[,,2]<-dt2
datos[,,3]<-dt3
pa<-param(datos, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
p1<-fmboxplot_0(1,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
p2<-fmboxplot_0(2,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
p3<-fmboxplot_0(3,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
outliers_i<-c()
r1<-fmboxplot_i0(dt1, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r1$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
r2<-fmboxplot_i0(dt2, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r2$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
r3<-fmboxplot_i0(dt3, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r3$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
gridExtra::grid.arrange(p1,p2,p3,r1$plot, r2$plot, r3$plot, nrow = 2)

tabla0_1<-rates0(pa$outliers,outliers_i)

ssm <- multimodel1(n_outliers = 10)

dt1 <- ssm[[1]]@X; dt2 <- ssm[[2]]@X; dt3 <- ssm[[3]]@X;

datos <- array(dim=c(100,50,3))
datos[,,1]<-dt1
datos[,,2]<-dt2
datos[,,3]<-dt3
pa<-param(datos, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
p1<-fmboxplot(1,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
p2<-fmboxplot(2,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
p3<-fmboxplot(3,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
outliers_i<-c()
r1<-fmboxplot_i(dt1, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r1$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
r2<-fmboxplot_i(dt2, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r2$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
r3<-fmboxplot_i(dt3, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r3$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
gridExtra::grid.arrange(p1,p2,p3,r1$plot, r2$plot, r3$plot, nrow = 2)

tabla1_1<-rates(pa$outliers,outliers_i)

dt1 <- ssm[[1]]@X; dt2 <- ssm[[2]]@X; dt3 <- ssm[[3]]@X; 

datos <- array(dim=c(100,50,3))
datos[,,1]<-dt1
datos[,,2]<-dt2
datos[,,3]<-dt3
pa<-param(datos, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
p1<-fmboxplot(1,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
p2<-fmboxplot(2,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
p3<-fmboxplot(3,pa$q1,pa$q3,pa$w1,pa$w3,pa$sdata,pa$outliers)
outliers_i<-c()
r1<-fmboxplot_i(dt1, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r1$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
r2<-fmboxplot_i(dt2, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r2$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
r3<-fmboxplot_i(dt3, t, rangeval, nbasis, norder)
for (i in r3$outliers){if(!is.element(i,outliers_i)){outliers_i<-c(outliers_i,i)}}
gridExtra::grid.arrange(p1,p2,p3,r1$plot, r2$plot, r3$plot, nrow = 2)

tabla8_1<-rates(pa$outliers,outliers_i)
